titles.title: To inform the Senate that a quorum of the House has assembled and of the election of the Speaker and the Clerk.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 1/4/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Informs the Senate that Nancy Pelosi has been elected Speaker of the House and that Karen L. Haas has been elected Clerk.
